des: "This is a dry rub that can be used on all meats, fish and vegetables. It is slightly sweet with a hint of heat."
ins: Place the cumin, ground coriander, curry powder, white pepper, ground ginger, allspice, cayenne pepper, seasoned salt, paprika, brown sugar, dry mustard, ground mace, and crushed rosemary in a food processor. Process the spice mixture until thoroughly blended. Store in an airtight container at room temperature.
